  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Herbivore Bait",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "食草动物诱饵",
    "TencentChinese": "食草动物诱饵",
    "TraditionalChinese": "草食者誘餌"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A specialist <span class=\"name name-stellar\">bait</span> for <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">herbivores</span>. Use the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Analysis Visor</span> to discover the bait preferences of specific creatures.<br><br>Created in a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Nutrient Processor</span> from <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Faecium</span> and <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">harvestable plants</span>.<br><br>Can be further processed in the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Nutrient Processor</span> to create <span class=\"name name-stellar\">new bait types</span>.<br><br>Feeding using the correct bait will allow creatures to be <VAL_ON>ridden<> or <VAL_ON>harvested<>. Chose bait type from the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种专业<span class=\"name name-stellar\">诱饵</span>，适用于<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">食草动物</span>。使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>发现特定生物的诱饵偏好。<br><br>用<span class=\"name name-technology\">营养处理器</span>制作，材料是<span class=\"name name-fuel\">屎球菌</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">可采集植物</span>。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">营养处理器</span>中进一步加工来制作<span class=\"name name-stellar\">新的诱饵类型</span>。<br><br>使用正确的诱饵喂食后，可<VAL_ON>骑乘<>或<VAL_ON>捕捉<>动物。从快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）中选择诱饵类型。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种专业<span class=\"name name-stellar\">诱饵</span>，适用于<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">食草动物</span>。使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>发现特定生物的诱饵偏好。<br><br>用<span class=\"name name-technology\">营养处理器</span>制作，材料是<span class=\"name name-fuel\">屎球菌</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">可采集植物</span>。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">营养处理器</span>中进一步加工来制作<span class=\"name name-stellar\">新的诱饵类型</span>。<br><br>使用正确的诱饵喂食后，可<VAL_ON>骑乘<>或<VAL_ON>捕捉<>动物。从快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）中选择诱饵类型。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "專門的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">誘餌</span>，專為<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">草食生物</span>所用。利用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析護目鏡</span>即可了解特定生物偏好哪一種誘餌。<br><br>利用<span class=\"name name-technology\">營養處理器</span>製造，原料是<span class=\"name name-fuel\">屎菌</span>與<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">可採收的植物</span>。<br><br>可在<span class=\"name name-technology\">營養處理器</span>中進一步處理，製造<span class=\"name name-stellar\">新種類的誘餌</span>。<br><br>餵食正確的誘餌，即可<VAL_ON>騎乘<>或<VAL_ON>採收<>生物。利用快捷選單（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）可選擇誘餌種類。"
  },
